-- BNP Aims to Double Latin America Sales in Three or Four Years, Echos Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-06-21T04:42:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/bnp-aims-to-double-latin-america-sales-in-three-or-four-years-echos-says.html

          
          
             BNP Paribas SA is aiming to double
its Latin American revenue of 300 million euros last year within
three or four years, Les Echos reported, citing Louis Bazire,
head of Brazilian operations.  
          
          


  


        